    0x01
This docker based Ci-Cd aims to integrate all necessary for EPITECH in order to
 make life easier by automating some repetitives tasks you might end up having
 to do.

    0x02
List of all required actions this tool need to do:
 - Coding style check (within the action yaml file, through the official
    docker image)
 - Build test (verify that no build errors occures)
 - Unit tests (run a defined .sh file)
 - Documentation building (for C/C++, using doxide and mkdocs)
 - Discord integration (send message using WebHooks to get action report)
 - Repository mirroring (to school repo)

    0x03
List of actions I would like this tool to do:
 - [ ] Gitleaks: Check for forgoten plain text passwords, API keys...
 - [ ] Discord bot integration (control the actions through discord bot, server
    control, users management, repos creation...)